title.narrative: TA to the Ministry of Power, Government of India - CONTRACT - KPMG

description.narrative: This activity (TA to the Ministry of Power, Government of India - CONTRACT - KPMG) is a component of Supporting Structural Reform in the Indian Power Sector reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £9,982,918. This component benefits India, and works in the following sector(s): Environmental policy and administrative management, Energy generation, renewable sources - multiple technologies. , with the following implementing partners: KPMG India, KPMG LLP. The start date is 01-08-2013 and the end date is 31-03-2022.
